<h2>Your Order Has Been Delivered! 📦✅</h2>

<p>Hi {{customerName}},</p>

<p>Your order <strong>#{{orderNumber}}</strong> from <strong>{{sellerName}}</strong> has been delivered.</p>

<div class="success-box">
  <div class="summary-row"><strong>Delivered On:</strong> {{deliveredDate}}</div>
  <div class="summary-row"><strong>Order Total:</strong> GH₵ {{totalAmount}}</div>
</div>

